*ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r5 (17 Apr 2004)

  17 Apr 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org>
  +files/ppc-sources-crypto.CAN-2004-0177.patch,
  +files/ppc-sources-crypto.CAN-2004-0178.patch,
  -ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r4.ebuild, +ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r5.ebuild:
  Added patches for the CAN-2004-0010, CAN-2004-0177 and CAN-2004-0178
  vulnerabilities.

*ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r4 (15 Apr 2004)

  15 Apr 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r3.ebuild,
  ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r4.ebuild,
  files/ppc-sources-crypto.CAN-2004-0109.patch:
  Version bump for the CAN-2004-0109 issue; bug #47881.

  12 Apr 2004; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org>
  ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r3.ebuild:
  Add eutils to inherit.

*ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r3 (19 Feb 2004)

  19 Feb 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r3.ebuild:
  Added the patch for the mremap/munmap vulnerability. Bug #42024. Old
  versions removed.

*ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r2 (08 Jan 2004)

  08 Jan 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r2.ebuild,
  files/ppc-sources-crypto.CAN-2003-0985.patch,
  files/ppc-sources-crypto.rtc_fix.patch:
  Version bumped. Added patches to address the security vulnerabilities in bugs
  #37292 and #37317.

  15 Dec 2003; <spider@gentoo.org> ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r1.ebuild,
  ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20.ebuild:
  QA: fixing chown user.group to user:group, bug #35127

*ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r1 (02 Dec 2003)

  02 Dec 2003; Brian Jackson <iggy@gentoo.org>
  ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20-r1.ebuild:
  Version bump for the 'do_brk' vulnerability.

  01 Dec 2003; Brian Jackson <iggy@gentoo.org>
  ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20.ebuild, files/do_brk_fix.patch:
  Fix for the 'do_brk' vulnerability.

  10 Mar 2003; Olivier Reisch <doctomoe@gentoo.org> ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20.ebuild:
  Marked 'ppc' stable.

*ppc-sources-crypto-2.4.20 (03 Feb 2003)

  03 Feb 2003; Olivier Reisch <doctomoe@gentoo.org> all:
  First ppc crypto kernel release. Basically a 2.4.20-ben5 with
  cryptoapi-0.1.0, cryptoloop 0.0.1-pre1 and loop-jari patch for 2.4.20
